                           <forename>Peter</forename>, son of <persName>
                              <forename>Alan</forename> de
                     <surname>Roston</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, the whole of their toft in <placeName key="place_103320">Roston</placeName> 
                  and half of a perch of land at <placeName key="place_103084">Boudalemun</placeName>, and all their right in six bovate which they 
                  hold of the King in capite.
                  (<origDate when="1290" precision="low">c. 1290</origDate>.)
